    "Participants were recruited from McGill University's study pool.",
    "Each of the 42 participants was fluent in English and free of major neurological or psychiatric disorders.",
    "Participants were on average 20 years old (SD = 1.4) and had 14.6 years of education (SD = 1.1).",
    "Thirty-seven of the participants were female.",
    "2021) investigated age-related changes in memory on a cued retrieval task and an openended task."
